{"tid":1458810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流動放映會:以tvb作為武器","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:00.000Z","uid":99018,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b0182fe076a7f475009a796982474e8c485430ef","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"對唔住响聽日入機場前開左個唔關事既post。<br />\n亦都對上一個開既post話唔再開post戴翻個頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntvb朝早同630新聞係大量刪減係無可改變既事實，佢會响最多人睇既時候以剪接事實去誤導市民。<br />\n但直播呢？tvb記者係有無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地有cut唔切既直播畫面，有袁志偉瞓撚左嗰陣出到既真&bull;新聞，呢啲全部都係credit to tvb。<br />\n如果我地用呢啲片cut出黎响街站到播呢？<br />\n首先班信tvb既會繼續信，因為係的確係tvb。<br />\n而亦都可以比人直接睇倒佢地平時睇唔倒既tvb，諗下點解佢地平時睇tvb睇唔倒呢啲嘢。<br />\n當然亦可能比人屈我地做假，<br />\n但應該可以係tvb度揾翻official既出處？<br />\n利申:唔識相關嘢，但希望有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceb10d5410c5567e104ffafb1612c4c9ad68949","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"十連後唔推"},{"pid":"e4a8b0c193e4096537bd39ac7f379e704aeacaae","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3b612c4ca0c7adb977f90361cabb2a688524b6e1","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cb398e127c3832c11ad8fc1ee0108a0e98c39124","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"63c5fb8fc61ec6c5255e799be63f0af3f12ee2fc","tid":1458810,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1a6ebf471d1bdecdff927141a05507ed40e102","tid":1458810,"uid":99018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:08:00.000Z"