19-08-12T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68e97d1e7fe62c16d3a7e9ed2d8fb5ac3457ada7","tid":1458810,"uid":304366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"52145ebdca222b1b17afa7a11c862ac90251adf0","tid":1458810,"uid":304366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"以子之矛攻子之盾"},{"pid":"b617c78dab711f614bbef50e8619283a9ed258f0","tid":1458810,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"Sorry借位求推<br />\n<br />\n突發！ 816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d23ec65215745c3ff2bf5eca36fcc25d6e00079a","tid":1458810,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"❗各位放映人士注意⚠❗❗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣幫手:<br />\n- 有資源或金錢既善長，可以提供放映設備<br />\n- 有時間又經常發惡夢既義士手足，可以去落各區放映<br />\n- 經過見到有人放映，請邀請佢地，一齊搞大佢先可以遍地開花 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要啲咩物資?<br />\n- 流動投影機 / 電視<br />\n- Projector Screen (用電視就唔洗)<br />\n- 座枱<br />\n- 流動電源 <br />\n- Speaker <br />\n<br />\n如果想支持我地嘅活動：<br />\n可以支持我地眾籌嘅活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/18區連儂放映會基金/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F18%E5%8D%80%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%2F&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=4a4f1f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/18區連儂放映會基金/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊道搞放映會比較好? 幾點擺好?<br />\n- 連儂牆既位置最好﹐因為又唔怕落雨，自己人又多<br />\n- 時間上，建議選擇番人流比較多既時間，一黎人多冇咁易俾人搞，二黎比較有效率<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n播啲咩片? <br />\n📹<br />\n呢道有個 DataBase將啲片以字幕/主題/長度/媒體/發佈日期做分類，節省搵片時間，亦可以唔同地點播放唔同既片段 📹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n✅影片下載教學: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H1p3ix&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=1c1b3266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix</a> <br />\n<br />\n✅中英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KpIbsA&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=30c1fe89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA</a> <br />\n✅純中字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YXU1lY&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=1c1ccdea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY</a><br />\n✅純英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OQyTu6&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=cb1515cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6</a><br />\n✅直播/冇字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yPNCdE&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=b5e17bac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有啲咩法律問題?<br />\n<br />\nBy Law&rsquo;s Friend:<br />\n- 擺街放新聞應該要擺邊？<br />\n（Projector / Projecting Screen)<br />\nAnywhere that can allow reasonable passage of pedestrians after setting up<br />\n<br />\n- 使唔使申請?<br />\nLess than 30 ppl no need<br />\n<br />\n- 多過幾多人會變非法集會?<br />\nNot unlawful assembly if no action that make other people reasonably worry abt breach of peace. But could be unauthorised assembly if more than 30 ppl. <br />\n<br />\n- 遇到警察應該點處理？<br />\nIf the police wanna record ID number and name, they can <br />\nBut other than that, they shouldn&rsquo;t be able to do anything <br />\n<br />\n- 如到對家動手可以點?<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why it is better to have more ppl doing this together, and whenever there are quarrels, there should be ppl filming <br />\n<br />\n- 被檢控後可以點?<br />\nFind a lawyer once you get arrested, before the arrival of lawyer don&rsquo;t say anything to police apart from name and hkid no.It is not so soon that one is prosecuted<br />\n<br />\n獲得最新18區連儂放映資訊:<br />\nFacebook Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/fb18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffb18districts&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=8ae7975b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fb18districts</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F18districts&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9ce0d5e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/18districts</a>"}]}